    All Diablo 2 Resurrected Set Items

    This is a searchable, filterable, sortable database of all Diablo 2 Resurrected Sets and Set Items. It shows the latest data from Resurrected v3.0 - Reign of the Warlock (where indicated), and otherwise uses data from Diablo 2 v1.14 LoD. You may search, filter, or sort by parent set, completion bonuses, stat modifiers, quality level, treasure class and more.
    Clears all active filters and searches.
    Start typing...
    Combining filter buttons with a search (or vice versa) is the most powerful way to filter.
    Filter items by their item type.
    Note that only one item type filter can be active at any time.
    Filter items that belong to a given parent set
    Note that only one 'part of set' filter can be active at any time.
    Filter by utility properties and/or miscellaneous item qualities.
    Filter by offensive type magical properties.
    Filter by defensive type magical properties.
    Filter by + to Skills magical properties.
    Filter by miscellaneous properties.
    Sort your filter selection by a number of options.
    Change viewing settings and other options.
    View results in a more traditional manner with a full-width area.
    View results with full tooltip detail & statistics on larger tiles.
    View results with reduced detail on more numerous, smaller tiles.
